":"","description":"","id":"https://mokurin000.github.io/blog/","path":"/blog/","title":"Blog"},"https://mokurin000.github.io/blog/hello-world/":{"body":"多年前，笔者用 AlanDecode/Maverick 搭建了第一个博客，奈何其中主题已经多年无人维护，故迁移至 zola + tabi 。\n其中博文多数已过时，部分为（与社区伙伴合作）的译文。这篇博客既是新的篇章，也是与过去的自己作一次告别。","description":"第一篇博客","id":"https://mokurin000.github.io/blog/hello-world/","path":"/blog/hello-world/","title":"你好，世界"},"https://mokurin000.github.io/projects/":{"body":"","description":"","id":"https://mokurin000.github.io/projects/","path":"/projects/","title":"Projects"},"https://mokurin000.github.io/projects/frigate-scripts/":{"body":"在 Arch Linux + NVIDIA 独显笔记本上部署 Frigate 的一些记录。\n软件前置\n硬件要求\n该方案相比于之前的丐版方案，需要更新的硬件才能解决种种兼容或性能问题。\n笔者测试环境：\n使用的文件\ninit.sh\nyolo_nas_s.onnx\n由于禁止分发转换后的模型，建议使用 Colab 运行官方 Notebook 获取：\nhttps://colab.research.google.com/github/blakeblackshear/frigate/blob/dev/notebooks/YOLO_NAS_Pretrained_Export.ipynb\ndocker-compose.yml\n-tensorrt 镜像仅 NVIDIA GPU 加速需要，AMD / Intel GPU 不需要。\nconfig.yaml\n此处以乐橙（IMOU）摄像头为例。\n大多数摄像头对应的 RTSP 地址都能在 iSpy 文档中找到。\n另外，乐橙摄像头要求 Wi-Fi 密码同时包含字母和数字，否则无法连接。\nFrigate 在配置方面的文档较为零散，需要同时参考完整参考配置和相关 Issue。\n如何彻底关闭服务\n如何通过命令行重启服务（不推荐）","description":"在 Arch Linux NVIDIA 笔记本上部署 Frigate、RTSP 摄像头与 ONNX 检测模型的记录。","id":"https://mokurin000.github.io/projects/frigate-scripts/","path":"/projects/frigate-scripts/","title":"Frigate + NVIDIA 显卡笔记本的部署"}},"docInfo":{"https://mokurin000.github.io/":{"body":3,"description":0,"path":0,"title":2},"https://mokurin000.github.io/archive/":{"body":0,"description":0,"path":1,"title":1},"https://mokurin000.github.io/blog/":{"body":0,"description":0,"path":1,"title":1},"https://mokurin000.github.io/blog/hello-world/":{"body":3,"description":0,"path":3,"title":0},"https://mokurin000.github.io/projects/":{"body":0,"description":0,"path":1,"title":1},"https://mokurin000.github.io/projects/frigate-scripts/":{"body":25,"description":5,"path":3,"title":2}},"length":6},"lang":"English"}